b'16. God Bless, and I hope you all have a great day. Remember - if you want to walk on water, you have got to get out of the boat.'
b'15. Your passion, dedication and love are the heartbeat of this nation - and underscore what could happen when we stand united.'
b'14. For my mom, my granddad, and everyone else who sacrificed so much so the next generation could live a better life - I say thank you.'
b'13. I am working every day to bring quality education, good jobs & the American Dream back to those who may not have experienced them yet'
b'12. That vision must continue to guide us into the future. To truly help us all, we must offer a hand to those in need.'
b'11. Our great nation was built on the dreams and ideals of a group of people who recognized that all men are created equal'
b'10. We can come together, and invest in our communities, encourage private dollars to help rebuild and restore.'
b'9. Let\xe2\x80\x99s recognize the manufacturing boom in states like SC, and reemphasize technical training, apprenticeships, and good, well paying jobs'
b'8. Every child must have access to a quality education. Unemployment, incarceration, dropout rates - all linked to educational achievement'
b'7. To turn back on the light at the end of the tunnel, and strengthen our nation from the ground up.'
b'6. And so, its up to us to bring it back to those millions of families across America who are desperately seeking a chance at success'
b'5. When you can\xe2\x80\x99t see beyond your own block, when you don\xe2\x80\x99t know what\xe2\x80\x99s possible, the American Dream starts to fade.'
b'4. I grew up in a place like that, and have seen both the short- and long-term effects this can bring.'
b'3. While we are the greatest nation on earth, we still have too many people living in poverty and in communities where hope has evaporated'
b'2. We must stand together, move forward together, and find solutions together.'
b'1. I stand for opportunity. For the belief that every single person in this country has greatness inside them waiting to be unleashed.'
